enb_long_title: United Nations Climate Change Conference - Bali
sentences: In its conclusions (FCCC/SBI/2007/L.25), the SBI took note of the information contained in the compilation and synthesis of the supplementary information submitted by Annex I parties under Protocol Article 7.2.

It also notes that not all Annex I Protocol parties have provided all the information that addresses inter alia , the concerns of developing country parties and requests them to provide this information in their next national communications.
